'''Filchner Mountains''' ({{coord|72|3|S|7|40|E|}}) is a [[mountain range]] 11 km (7 mi) southwest of [[Drygalski Mountains]], at the west end of the [[Orvin Mountains]] of [[Queen Maud Land]].
